  "prompt": "Where can I learn SAP ABAP in Bangalore with placement?",
  "response": "Learning SAP ABAP in Bangalore with placement opportunities can be facilitated through several reputable institutes. Here are a few options:\n\n1. **ATOS India**:\n   - They offer SAP ABAP training and have a strong placement record. Their trainers are experienced professionals and their course includes both theoretical and practical components.\n   - Website: [ATOS India](https://atos.net/en/india)\n\n2. **Keltron Knowledge Centre**:\n   - This institute provides comprehensive SAP ABAP training along with placement assistance. They focus on real-time examples and hands-on sessions.\n   - Website: [Keltron Knowledge Centre](http://www.keltron.in)\n\n3. **eMexo Technologies**:\n   - They offer SAP ABAP training with placement support. Their curriculum includes working on real-time projects which can greatly enhance your practical knowledge.\n   - Website: [eMexo Technologies](https://www.emexotechnologies.com/)\n\n4. **Techavera Solutions Pvt Ltd**:\n   - They provide industry-oriented SAP ABAP training and have a dedicated placement cell to assist students in finding suitable job opportunities.\n   - Website: [Techavera Solutions Pvt Ltd](https://techavera.in/)\n\n5. **Zenfotec**:\n   - Known for their strong placement support and high-quality training sessions in SAP ABAP, Zenfotec leverages experienced trainers and practical training techniques.\n   - Website: [Zenfotec](https://www.zenfotec.com/)\n\nBefore enrolling, it is advisable to check the current reviews, speak to alumni, and confirm the placement support to ensure that it aligns with your career objectives.",
